To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private BeltHold _belthold;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_belthold = BeltHold(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_belthold.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "BeltHold Period", _belthold.Period);
    Plot("My Indicators", "BeltHold Current", _belthold.Current);
}
# In Initialize()
symbol = self.AddEquity("SPY").Symbol
self.belthold = self.BeltHold(symbol)

# In OnData()
if self.belthold.IsReady:
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "BeltHold Period", self.belthold.Period)
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "BeltHold Current", self.belthold.Current)

For more information about plotting indicators, see Plotting Indicators.
